  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay Introduction:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the day, you can build and upgrade your base, recruit followers, purchase items, or advance technologies to strengthen your forces. Strategic allocation of time and gold is crucial for efficient progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At night, your recruited followers will automatically engage enemies in battles using auto-battler mechanics — fully automated and requires no manual control. Survive the onslaught by optimizing your daytime preparations!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple followers with diverse skills  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/12a9cd0a12dc38ebbddc27d606515c5e.poster.avif?t=1740362496\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/12a9cd0a12dc38ebbddc27d606515c5e.webm?t=1740362496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/12a9cd0a12dc38ebbddc27d606515c5e.mp4?t=1740362496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buildings with various functions </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/617397814e5bbbce98af476d4bab620d.poster.avif?t=1740362496\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/617397814e5bbbce98af476d4bab620d.webm?t=1740362496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/617397814e5bbbce98af476d4bab620d.mp4?t=1740362496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Items with different effects</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/5ebbab417e12ec9b37115e09cca38afd.poster.avif?t=1740362496\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/5ebbab417e12ec9b37115e09cca38afd.webm?t=1740362496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/5ebbab417e12ec9b37115e09cca38afd.mp4?t=1740362496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay Introduction:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the day, you can build and upgrade your base, recruit followers, purchase items, or advance technologies to strengthen your forces. Strategic allocation of time and gold is crucial for efficient progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At night, your recruited followers will automatically engage enemies in battles using auto-battler mechanics — fully automated and requires no manual control. Survive the onslaught by optimizing your daytime preparations!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple followers with diverse skills  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/12a9cd0a12dc38ebbddc27d606515c5e.poster.avif?t=1740362496\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/12a9cd0a12dc38ebbddc27d606515c5e.webm?t=1740362496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/12a9cd0a12dc38ebbddc27d606515c5e.mp4?t=1740362496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buildings with various functions </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/617397814e5bbbce98af476d4bab620d.poster.avif?t=1740362496\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/617397814e5bbbce98af476d4bab620d.webm?t=1740362496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947410/extras/617397814e5bbbce98af476d